    <name>Archive</name>
    <summary>Track progress across media</summary>
    <description>
        <p>Archive can track progress and also work as a launcher for files and URIs for its entries and have categories for them, such as manga, anime, or TV shows, etc.</p>
        <p>Some features:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Categories</li>
          <li>Notes for entries</li>
          <li>Filtering by status ("in progress", "finished", "planned"), tags, file name</li>
          <li>Hiding individual entries and categories</li>
          <li>Entry color themeing</li>
          <li>Adding CBZ files, videos, and folders as entries</li>
          <li>Drag and drop for adding entries and for reordering categories</li>
          <li>Sorting by random, alphabetical order, date, or launched order</li>
          <li>Custom covers for entries</li>
          <li>Launching commands/URIs</li>
        </ul>
    </description>
